    {
      "id": "kdslJnScrvKp3pS4Bv-PE",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 365.751220703125,
      "y": 221.40274047851562,
      "width": 877.3194580078125,
      "height": 1400,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b2s",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1988655322,
      "version": 858,
      "versionNonce": 961371782,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1782364292676,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Requirements :\nq. imp features?\na. download file, upload file, resumable download? yes, view files in a folder, create folder, \nsimultaneous file edits? no\nshare files with friends\n\nq. scale?\na. 10m DAU, 50 m MAU\n\nq. Any existing system?\na. auth and cloud infra\n\nq. file size?\na. max 1 GB\n\nq. storage per user?\na. 10 GB\n\nq. file types=all\n\nq. encryption = yes\n\nFunctional requirements:\ndownload file, \nupload file, \nresumable download\nview files in a folder\ncreate folder, \nsimultaneous file edits? no\nshare files with friends\nNotification when file is edited\n\nNFR:\nAvaliable : 99.999\nlow latency : less than 500 ms for 500 kb file\nRelaiable\nScalable\n\nBack of envelope calc:\n\nDAU : 10m\nper user : 10 GB\n\nStrage:\n10m * 10 GB = 10^8 GB = 100 PB daily\n10000 PB of total storage\n\ntraffic:\nDAU 10m\n10:1 read to write ratio\n20 : 2\n\n20 * 10^6 / ~ 10^5 = 200 write ps\nreads = 2000 rps\n\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Requirements :\nq. imp features?\na. download file, upload file, resumable download? yes, view files in a folder, create folder, \nsimultaneous file edits? no\nshare files with friends\n\nq. scale?\na. 10m DAU, 50 m MAU\n\nq. Any existing system?\na. auth and cloud infra\n\nq. file size?\na. max 1 GB\n\nq. storage per user?\na. 10 GB\n\nq. file types=all\n\nq. encryption = yes\n\nFunctional requirements:\ndownload file, \nupload file, \nresumable download\nview files in a folder\ncreate folder, \nsimultaneous file edits? no\nshare files with friends\nNotification when file is edited\n\nNFR:\nAvaliable : 99.999\nlow latency : less than 500 ms for 500 kb file\nRelaiable\nScalable\n\nBack of envelope calc:\n\nDAU : 10m\nper user : 10 GB\n\nStrage:\n10m * 10 GB = 10^8 GB = 100 PB daily\n10000 PB of total storage\n\ntraffic:\nDAU 10m\n10:1 read to write ratio\n20 : 2\n\n20 * 10^6 / ~ 10^5 = 200 write ps\nreads = 2000 rps\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
