      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1782400640727,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Validation of blocks : validate for size, corruptd data etc\nde-duplication of blocks - Chceksum of block and dont store duplicate blocks\nvirus scanning - VirusScanner \nSearch index - ElasticSearch\nVersion manager - Move older versions to glacier after a certain time/ delete them\n\nAll the above tasks happen asynchronoulsy\n\n\nPermission manager : userA reader and userB writer",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Validation of blocks : validate for size, corruptd data etc\nde-duplication of blocks - Chceksum of block and dont store duplicate blocks\nvirus scanning - VirusScanner \nSearch index - ElasticSearch\nVersion manager - Move older versions to glacier after a certain time/ delete them\n\nAll the above tasks happen asynchronoulsy\n\n\nPermission manager : userA reader and userB writer",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
